flexitimer, installation prior to compiling code: https://playground.arduino.cc/Main/FlexiTimer2/
adjustment operation prior to running
    uncomment ADJUST, make and run
    comment ADJUST, uncomment VERIFY
    measure real sites and set to real_site[4][3], make and run
    comment VERIFY, make and run
movement combo one
    stand up, wait 2 sec
    forward 5 steps, wait 2 sec
    backward 5 steps, wait 2 sec
    turn right, wait 2 sec
    turn left, wait 2 sec
    wave hand, wait 2 sec
    shake hand, wait 2 sec
    sit down, wait 2 sec
    back to 1
